Polysyllabic words: ( med 3 letters at least: ) 16 

Long sentences (10+ words) = 4

A = avsnitts-längd = words / sentences
A = ( 72 words) / ( 4 sentences ) 
A = 18

We now calculate the final LIX:
( 16/72) * 100 = 22
( 18 / 100) * 4 = 0.72 
The equation is then: 
(22) + 0.72 = 22.72